{"tid":1477813,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【求教高手】誠哥A1個抗止暴力標誌真正意思","createTime":"2019-08-16T09:01:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T09:20:52.000Z","uid":243790,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c9152ad04658801ee62cf8535b7b32afeec53904","tid":1477813,"uid":243790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T09:01:35.000Z","msg":"食晏同個高人吹水，傾誠哥個A1全版廣告。「因果由國，容港治己」、「義憤」相信大家都睇到。不過高人仲叫我留意吓個抗止暴力標誌。話説個紅圈既不置中，又不完全覆蓋「暴力」二字。究竟係要止什麼，抗什麼？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LqZBY2i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLqZBY2i.jpg&h=8b9a9b00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n跟手佢些牙咗張圖俾我，紅圈外筆劃remove咗。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5Nzm986.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5Nzm986.jpg&h=2a302072&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n暴字無咗個日，好似變咗<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">兩個字</span></span>；力字無咗個鈎，又有啲似<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一個圖案</span></span>，好熟口面唔知喺邊支旗上面見過。小弟才疏學淺唔是好明，唔知有冇巴絲可以指點吓？究竟真正意思係要止什麼，抗什麼？"},{"pid":"cc6a62c9506f0f0a31fc7528cf0ab47aa596bd2b","tid":1477813,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T09:02:42.000Z","msg":"普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7cf1c5b83debd9f0bd1ea858c63f2843e5766e42","tid":1477813,"uid":27458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T09:04:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27d300c72e861c872b515cd5e5fcd767dc58d535","tid":1477813,"uid":222953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T09:04:53.000Z","msg":"禁共黨"},{"pid":"88c2870e275054cc4ca25f91c2d85e986b48507d","tid":1477813,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T09:05:58.000Z",